Amen!  But I'll have to admit, there are times when the whole evening is nothing but sitting and sitting... and sitting... with only the occasional heal needed... and then soon the buffs wear off so I re-buff everyone.  And continue to sit some more.  If we are hunting something that is fairly easy, then the life of a cleric can be boring.  But instead of taking out my knife and carving little trinkets out of the peices of wood I find near me, I'd really prefer to hit a little, blast a little.  You know, get some exercise.  I will have to admit that the most fun is to be had when the whole party goes through a totally bloody battle and I have to concentrate all my thoughts on keeping everyone alive.  But it's been a long, long time since I've seen such a battle.<br>
